transcript.title: Western Australia Election Result
transcript.content:
Canberra

The Prime Minister congratulates Colin Barnett on his re-election as the Premier of Western Australia.

The Gillard Government looks forward to continuing to work with the Barnett Government on a range of important initiatives which will benefit the people of Western Australia and recognise the importance that WA plays to the national economy.

The Prime Minister acknowledges Mark McGowan and the WA Labor team for their hard-fought campaign.
